Package: agentr
Type: Package
Title: Cognitive Core for Agentic Workflows in R
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver", 
           family = "Zhou",
           email = "oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Cognitive and human-interaction core for agentic workflows.
    The package represents agent state, supports human-in-the-loop scaffolding,
    and generates workflow specifications such as DAG-like plans and
    implementation-ready structures. It intentionally excludes communication
    backends and provider-specific LLM client code so that workflow reasoning
    can remain cleanly separated from execution and transport layers.
